what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Applied early_filter_decorrelate by creating independent CTEs for filtered dimensions (date, item, address) before main joins, pre-joined customer with demographics, created a CTE for store-warehouse state matching, and separated store_sales/web_sales filtering into separate CTEs to reduce join sizes early.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
